304
00:17:07,436 --> 00:17:08,421
Only you.

305
00:17:10,230 --> 00:17:11,514
You're so handsome,

306
00:17:11,514 --> 00:17:13,377
and you're serious about her.

307
00:17:13,377 --> 00:17:14,872
