308
00:17:14,872 --> 00:17:16,472
Huo Da, don't regret thia.

309
00:17:16,472 --> 00:17:18,453
I will use all my ability to pursue Jia Di.

310
00:17:20,034 --> 00:17:21,124
Very good.

311
00:17:21,124 --> 00:17:22,059
You and Jia Di.

312
00:17:22,059 --> 00:17:23,437
Yan Shu and I.

313
00:17:24,029 --> 00:17:25,691
It must be all God's preperation.

314
00:17:32,708 --> 00:17:34,014
Jia Di really loves you!

315
00:18:09,194 --> 00:18:10,445
Let me see the other exchange coupon!

316
00:18:12,968 --> 00:18:14,108
Take it out.

317
00:18:20,720 --> 00:18:22,155
~Give her happiness~

318
00:18:26,541 --> 00:18:27,781
You have seen through me.

319
00:18:28,901 --> 00:18:31,511
Yes. I've deceived you.

320
00:18:31,511 --> 00:18:33,150
Both of them are the same.

321
00:18:33,635 --> 00:18:34,782
You would've definitely picked

322
00:18:34,782 --> 00:18:36,448
the 'Give her Happiness' exchange coupon,

323
00:18:36,790 --> 00:18:38,213
and I could smoothly

324
00:18:38,213 --> 00:18:40,031
