Just go along with the play.

331
00:18:54,228 --> 00:18:55,592
Isn't it more touching?

332
00:18:58,216 --> 00:18:59,363
At least like this,

333
00:18:59,363 --> 00:19:01,294
I won't have to face the crying Ah Xin.

334
00:19:01,760 --> 00:19:03,280
She gets more annoying by the minute.

335
00:19:03,280 --> 00:19:04,621
I've toleranced enough of

336
00:19:04,621 --> 00:19:05,838
