338
00:19:20,951 --> 00:19:22,412
From now on,

339
00:19:22,412 --> 00:19:24,446
I will use all my capabilities to protect Jia Di.

340
00:19:41,556 --> 00:19:43,151
Don't forget...

341
00:19:46,087 --> 00:19:47,400
Give her happiness.

342
00:19:55,621 --> 00:19:57,279
Why did you do that?

343
00:19:58,672 --> 00:20:00,825
Why did you give Jia Di to Huo Yan?

344
00:20:03,387 --> 00:20:05,278
