Jia Di wouldn't be in trouble, would she?

384
00:23:34,755 --> 00:23:35,614
Hello?

385
00:23:35,614 --> 00:23:36,708
Hello, General Manager.

386
00:23:36,708 --> 00:23:37,989
I am Jia Di's mom.

387
00:23:37,989 --> 00:23:39,615
Is Jia Di with you?

388
00:23:40,217 --> 00:23:40,879
Auntie,

389
00:23:40,879 --> 00:23:42,554
Jia Di is not here.

390
00:23:44,411 --> 00:23:45,973
I thought she was resting at home,

391
00:23:45,973 --> 00:23:46,787
but when I came back

392
00:23:46,787 --> 00:23:48,347
she wasn't here.

393
00:23:48,347 --> 00:23:50,113
Yesterday, Huo Da hurt her so badly,

394
00:23:50,113 --> 00:23:51,880
where would she go?

395
00:23:52,541 --> 00:23:53,550
I called her cellphone just now,

396
00:23:53,550 --> 00:23:55,318
but she didn't pick up.

397
00:23:55,538 --> 00:23:57,957
Then... I know she's a very earnest child,

398
00:23:57,957 --> 00:23:59,505
so she won't do silly things,

399
00:23:59,505 --> 00:24:01,508
but... I'm still very worried.

400
00:24:02,146 --> 00:24:02,883
Auntie,

401
00:24:02,883 --> 00:24:04,654
I think I know where Jia Di is.

402
00:24:05,677 --> 00:24:06,364
Mr. Huo,

403
00:24:06,364 --> 00:24:07,741
have you been sleeping well lately?

404
00:24:10,630 --> 00:24:11,540
Not that well.

405
00:24:11,996 --> 00:24:13,411
Not that well. Okay.

406
00:24:13,695 --> 00:24:15,522
What about eating? Normal?

407
00:24:18,084 --> 00:24:19,150
I don't have much of an appetite.

408
00:25:05,111 --> 00:25:06,112
Wear it.

409
00:25:06,112 --> 00:25:07,551
Don't catch a cold.

410
00:25:09,221 --> 00:25:10,377
Auntie is very worried about you.

411
00:25:10,377 --> 00:25:11,957
She told me to find you.

412
00:25:15,954 --> 00:25:17,083
Don't forget.

413
00:25:17,083 --> 00:25:18,098
There are still a lot of people

414
00:25:18,098 --> 00:25:20,034
