415
00:25:22,520 --> 00:25:24,228
They don't seem to be back yet.

416
00:25:27,147 --> 00:25:29,049
I want to stay here and wait for them to come back.

417
00:25:31,118 --> 00:25:33,209
I want to know why he changed so drastically.

418
00:25:35,570 --> 00:25:36,368
You may see things

419
00:25:36,368 --> 00:25:37,669
