420
00:25:41,881 --> 00:25:44,457
At least I can work harder, right?

421
00:25:47,387 --> 00:25:50,714
Maybe we just didn't have a good talk.

422
00:25:50,714 --> 00:25:53,323
Or maybe he has something to tell me,

423
00:25:53,323 --> 00:25:56,621
but I spent too much time arguing with him.

424
00:25:56,621 --> 00:25:58,996
So I didn't give him a chance to talk.

425
00:25:59,323 --> 00:26:00,620
At least like this,

426
00:26:00,620 --> 00:26:03,106
I won't have to face a crying Ah Xin.

427
00:26:03,106 --> 00:26:04,959
She gets more annoying by the minute.

428
00:26:04,959 --> 00:26:06,294
I've tolerated enough of

429
00:26:06,294 --> 00:26:07,668
her childlike behaviour!

430
00:26:10,980 --> 00:26:11,824
Don't wait anymore.

431
00:26:11,824 --> 00:26:13,247
I'll take you back.

432
00:26:14,138 --> 00:26:16,110
I want to wait for him.

433
00:26:25,559 --> 00:26:27,283
Based on Huo Da's personality,

434
00:26:27,283 --> 00:26:28,812
if he doesn't want to turn back,

435
00:26:28,812 --> 00:26:31,218
I'm scared that you'll be hurt even deeper.

436
00:26:32,909 --> 00:26:36,113
You're scared that the Devil will think that I'm too scared to stand up,

437
00:26:36,113 --> 00:26:38,004
will use an even more despicable attitude towards me,

438
00:26:38,004 --> 00:26:39,752
and push me away, right?

439
00:26:42,524 --> 00:26:44,319
Actually, I know

440
00:26:44,319 --> 00:26:46,429
