442
00:26:49,710 --> 00:26:50,866
But in my heart,

443
00:26:50,866 --> 00:26:52,774
there has always been a voice

444
00:26:52,774 --> 00:26:54,997
telling me

445
00:26:54,997 --> 00:26:57,841
that when the Devil's very harsh on the outside,

446
00:26:59,914 --> 00:27:03,026
