453
00:27:18,864 --> 00:27:20,499
Even if he doesn't return to me,

454
00:27:20,499 --> 00:27:22,157
it's all right.

455
00:27:22,747 --> 00:27:24,453
I know that you'll get hurt,

456
00:27:24,453 --> 00:27:26,876
