458
00:27:37,763 --> 00:27:40,233
Exchange coupon for a 'Gold Fist.'

459
00:27:40,904 --> 00:27:42,406
If one day, Jia Di gets tired,

460
00:27:42,406 --> 00:27:44,847
you can exchange with the 10th Guy.

461
00:27:44,847 --> 00:27:46,499
Exchange what?

462
00:27:46,499 --> 00:27:48,421
Now that his fist has recovered,

463
00:27:48,421 --> 00:27:49,725
his hands are strong,

464
00:27:49,725 --> 00:27:52,827
