465
00:27:58,238 --> 00:27:59,954
I have said before

466
00:27:59,954 --> 00:28:02,173
that every part of me will believe in you.

467
00:28:02,173 --> 00:28:03,657
Even if you hurt deeper,

468
00:28:03,657 --> 00:28:05,531
