474
00:28:48,770 --> 00:28:49,627
Miss Yan Shu!

475
00:28:49,627 --> 00:28:51,037
Miss Yan Shu!

476
00:28:51,315 --> 00:28:53,192
Please let me see Huo Da.

477
00:28:53,564 --> 00:28:54,940
No way.

478
00:28:55,898 --> 00:28:58,178
I won't let you see Huo Da anymore.

479
00:29:01,771 --> 00:29:04,129
Since he has chosen me already,

480
00:29:04,129 --> 00:29:06,832
