491
00:29:34,508 --> 00:29:36,112
Whatever.

492
00:29:46,468 --> 00:29:47,743
Come back tomorrow.

493
00:29:47,743 --> 00:29:48,632
Jia Di,

494
00:29:48,632 --> 00:29:50,844
if you continue, you won't be able to take it.

495
00:29:54,813 --> 00:29:55,743
You think your determination

496
00:29:55,743 --> 00:29:58,196
