497
00:30:00,751 --> 00:30:03,082
I believe that one day, he'll soften.

498
00:30:15,173 --> 00:30:16,424
Yang Yan Shu,

499
00:30:16,424 --> 00:30:18,956
don't think of anything else.

500
00:30:18,956 --> 00:30:21,814
You can only be be Huo Da's accompaniment.

501
00:30:21,814 --> 00:30:25,986
When things get cleared up,

502
00:30:25,986 --> 00:30:27,177
you and Huo Da

503
00:30:27,177 --> 00:30:29,833
probably will have lost our loved ones.

504
00:30:31,429 --> 00:30:33,331
Even if it turns out like that,

505
00:30:33,605 --> 00:30:35,315
